TEXT(CAPA_EV (<<'END_OF_TEXT'));
If the elevator's descending speed is measured at 10 \{ $mPs_u \} at a given point, but its speed is decreasing by \{  spf( $accel    , "%0.1f" ) \} \{ $mPs2_u \}, what does the scale read?
END_OF_TEXT

